Installation Instruction for Attendance Utility.

================================================

version :1.0.3

1.Install python Executable [32 or 64 bit based system arch]
2.set system Enviornment Variable path as ;c:/python27; [installation folder of python]
3.create a folder in C Drive named as 'Orchid' and paste the folder zklib,biometric_sch and config.py file.
4.Open the file config.py > its dictionary format {},key,value pair,fill appropriate key with appropriate values
5.Run command prompt > type shell:startup > right click and create shortcut > specify the path of biometric_sch file which is in C:Orchid
6.Restart the system.
